    "Name": "Firestorm",
    "Details": "The Firestorm focuses on anti-infantry and anti-vehicle combat. Similar to the Shadow Cat, the Firestorm uses a single main weapon supported by several smaller ones. The right arm carries an Inner Sphere-produced plasma rifle fed by two tons of ammunition, while a plasma cannon mounted in the right torso and fed by one ton of ammunition provides additional power. Supporting these weapons are a flamer, micro pulse laser, and ER medium laser mounted in the left arm. Built on an endo-steel skeleton, the Firestorm uses a 250-rated extralight engine to reach a speed of 86 km/h. A MASC system mounted in the left torso allows it to sprint at speeds of 108 km/h. Seven improved jump jets let the 'Mech cover 210 meters in a jump. Protection is provided by nine tons of ferro-fibrous armor.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Upper</color>",
